original_font_information.description: Spinaker is based on French and UK lettering found on posters for travel by ship. Spinaker is a low contrast slightly wide sans serif design. Spinaker has a whimsy youthful sense of play to offer in addition to the expected utility that a sans design commonly offers. Spinaker is suitable for medium to large sizes.
